snippet: The White House said on Monday that it expects final enrollment numbers for private health care insurance under Obamacare in 2014 to be "substantially larger" than 6 million after a busy final weekend of in-person and online signups....

headline.print_headline: White House Sees Obamacare Sign-Ups 'Substantially Larger' Than Six Million
headline.main: White House Sees Obamacare Sign-Ups 'Substantially Larger' Than Six Million

lead_paragraph: The White House said on Monday that it expects final enrollment numbers for private health care insurance under Obamacare in 2014 to be "substantially larger" than 6 million after a busy final weekend of in-person and online signups.
